casebody.data:
Bingham McCUTCHEN, et al., petitioners,
v.
Hartwell HARRIS. No. 13-351. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 13, 2014.

Motion of New England Legal Foundation for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeal of California, Second Appellate District, denied.
